<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='524286' id='t-524286'>by people from around the world</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='525779' id='t-525779'>that want their phones to be doing 
something else in their afterlife,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='529072' id='t-529072'>so to speak.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='529826' id='t-529826'>And if the rest of the device
can be completely recycled,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='532755' id='t-532755'>then we believe it's
an entirely upcycled device.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:06
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='535471' id='t-535471'>So again, this didn't come
