<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='544294' id='t-544294'>that there's always
going to be enough there</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='546663' id='t-546663'>that you can build similar solutions</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='548474' id='t-548474'>that can be very effective
in new contexts.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:21
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='550540' id='t-550540'>Thank you very much.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 9:23
